      "content": "it does feel like my anxiety, honestly. i've been under so much stress at work lately and my heart's been racing a lot. but the nausea is making me a bit nervous. do u think i should really bother going to the A&E at this hour? it seems like a lot of drama if it's just stress again, and im mostly just tired.",
