    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's hard to tell if it's just the stress or something else. i actually have some propranolol left over from when my doctor prescribed it for my anxiety last year. do u think taking a pill of that might help settle my heart racing and the chest tightness so i can just sleep it off? i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to.",
