    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can see why you'd want to try to manage your symptoms with something familiar. Propranolol is a beta blocker, which can help with anxiety-related heart racing and chest tightness. However, I would advise against taking it without speaking to your doctor first, as they may have specific instructions or concerns. Additionally, propranolol can have side effects, especially when taken in large doses or without medical supervision. If you're still unsure, consider calling your doctor or a nurse hotline for guidance.",
      "source": "target",
